                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18130407-106-defend977 t18130407-106-punish545"></join>
               DEATH
            </rs>, aged 57.</p>
               <p>Second Middlesex jury, before Mr. Common Serjeant.</p>
